3
00:01:13,280 --> 00:01:14,720
He managed to avoid the penalty this time.

4
00:01:15,080 --> 00:01:16,160
Do you think he did it on purpose?

5
00:01:16,480 --> 00:01:17,480
How could it be such a coincidence?

6
00:01:20,720 --> 00:01:21,720
Then let him stay in the mental hospital

7
00:01:21,720 --> 00:01:22,720
