8
00:01:26,480 --> 00:01:27,200
So, what's next?

9
00:01:27,360 --> 00:01:28,120
What are you going to do?

10
00:01:32,320 --> 00:01:33,360
I'm going to get Xu Meng back.

11
00:01:37,680 --> 00:01:38,240
Good luck.

12
00:01:42,240 --> 00:01:43,560
How's the orphanage charity foundation

13
00:01:43,560 --> 00:01:44,480
