14
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:45,720
Almost done.

15
00:01:46,480 --> 00:01:47,920
When are you going to tell Ms. Xu?

16
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:13,320
Lu Xing,

17
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:15,760
