21
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:26,120
So you have to wake up soon.

22
00:02:26,720 --> 00:02:28,160
Let's go meet the baby together.

23
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:30,040
Okay?

24
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:49,040
Wenjie,

25
00:02:51,880 --> 00:02:53,560
It's not good for the baby

26
00:02:53,720 --> 00:02:54,720
