30
00:03:12,720 --> 00:03:13,880
I've talked to the doctor.

31
00:03:14,720 --> 00:03:16,840
His condition is improving.

32
00:03:17,720 --> 00:03:19,240
So, the most important thing for you now

33
00:03:19,640 --> 00:03:20,840
