34
00:03:23,720 --> 00:03:24,400
I will.

35
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:27,640
I still have to wait for him to wake up.

36
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:57,280
The shareholders are already

37
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:58,200
