47
00:04:17,240 --> 00:04:19,080
What can a young man do?

48
00:04:43,280 --> 00:04:43,720
Ladies and gentlemen,

49
00:04:44,160 --> 00:04:45,120
the former chairman,

50
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:46,320
