73
00:05:27,440 --> 00:05:28,280
Am I right?

74
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:29,600
Yes.

75
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:30,520
That's it.

76
00:05:30,520 --> 00:05:31,080
It makes sense.

77
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:32,080
You have to convince us.

78
00:05:32,200 --> 00:05:32,880
Yes.

79
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:45,560
I have 70% of the shares of Lin Group.

80
00:05:50,520 --> 00:05:51,160
