99
00:07:15,880 --> 00:07:17,320
Pack up and go there tonight.

100
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:18,280
I'm busy.

101
00:07:18,280 --> 00:07:19,560
I'm doing business for hundreds of millions per second.

102
00:07:19,800 --> 00:07:20,680
I'm busy.

103
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:23,200
