116
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:21,760
Thank you, Uncle Zhang.

117
00:08:21,880 --> 00:08:22,560
Just put it over there.

118
00:08:24,840 --> 00:08:25,640
I heard

119
00:08:26,520 --> 00:08:28,000
that Mr. Lin has been...

120
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:28,600
Uncle Zhang,

121
00:08:29,880 --> 00:08:31,360
I have to meet with the project team later.

122
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:32,520
Let's talk about other things

123
00:08:32,760 --> 00:08:33,720
